# AS Brokers Cursor Rules

- Default to React Server Components. Use use client only for forms, calculators, Framer Motion, or browser APIs.
- Data mutations: use Next.js Server Actions. No REST API routes for form or CRM submissions.
- Validation: Zod at all form and calculator boundaries.
- Styling: Tailwind only, mobile-first. Glassmorphism: bg-white/5, backdrop-blur-xl, ring-1 ring-white/10 for primary cards.
- Motion: respect prefers-reduced-motion everywhere.
- Everest: R100k minimum on voluntary products. Amethyst drawdown 2.5 to 17.5 percent. Show liquidity warning on voluntary product pages.
- Read agents.md and app/calculators/CONTEXT.md when changing business logic or formulas.
